About this item

  • ADJUSTABLE LED CEILING LIGHTS: The Juno LED adjustable recessed ceiling light is great for residential and light commercial applications; Use it as a shower light, kitchen ceiling light, or outdoor ceiling light
  • VERSATILE 5-IN-1 RECESSED LIGHT: LED light offers 5 white color temperatures (soft, warm, neutral, cool, and daylight) to create the right ambiance for any space; Gimbal is adjustable with up to 20 degrees of rotation making it great for angled ceilings
  • DURABLE RECESSED LED LIGHTS: Polycarbonate injection molded outer frame with steel back plate ensures excellent thermal management and durability; Features an all-in-one LED engine with polycarbonate lens that provides even illumination

From the manufacturer

What is Switchable Color Temperature?

Color temperature (Correlated Color Temperature, or CCT) is a numerical system for measuring color on a warm-to-cool spectrum. It is a measurement of the warmth or coolness of light that appears in a space. An integrated switch on each fixture allows the ability to change the color temperature. So whether you want a space to feel warm and cozy or cool and crisp, simply toggle the integrated switch to your desired setting and you are done!

Ratings and Listings

The Juno 4 inch adjustable downlight with 5CCT switchable white technology provides high-quality light output and efficiency featuring a switch for easy color temperature adjustment to choose between 2700K, 3000K, 3500K, 4000K, or 5000K. The downlight is CSA certified to US and Canadian safety standards; ENERGY STAR certified; Suitable for wet location; Air-Lox certified; NOM certified; Can be used to comply with California Title 24 Part 6 High Efficacy LED light Source Requirements.

What is Lumen Output?

Lumens refer to the measure light output or the brightness of a light. The higher the number, the more light is emitted.

Product Description

The Juno 4 inch adjustable downlight with 5CCT switchable white technology provides high-quality light output and efficiency featuring a switch for easy color temperature adjustment to choose between 2700K, 3000K, 3500K, 4000K, or 5000K. The canless design eliminates the need for recessed housings, making it easy to install and requires less labor. The adjustable gimbal allows for up to 20 degrees of rotation, making this version perfect for angled ceilings.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    5.0 out of 5 stars Matches Discontinued Lithonia Recessed Lights
    Reviewed in the United States on July 9, 2024
    Size: 4-InchColor: Matte WhiteVerified Purchase
    We were trying to find a match for the Lithonia Lighting 4 in. Selectable Color Temperature Recessed Lights (SKU #312186839) that we installed in our bedroom last year. We wanted to use the same recessed lights in our living room, but discovered the Lithonia recessed lights are either out of stock, or discontinued.

About this Item

  • ADJUSTABLE LED CEILING LIGHTS: The Juno LED adjustable recessed ceiling light is great for residential and light commercial applications; Use it as a shower light, kitchen ceiling light, or outdoor ceiling light
  • VERSATILE 5-IN-1 RECESSED LIGHT: LED light offers 5 white color temperatures (soft, warm, neutral, cool, and daylight) to create the right ambiance for any space; Gimbal is adjustable with up to 20 degrees of rotation making it great for angled ceilings
  • DURABLE RECESSED LED LIGHTS: Polycarbonate injection molded outer frame with steel back plate ensures excellent thermal management and durability; Features an all-in-one LED engine with polycarbonate lens that provides even illumination
  • EASY INSTALLATION: Canless design and steel spring clip make installation; Cut out template is provided to ensure a correct sized hole is cut into ceiling for proper installation; Wet rated and air-loc for showers, bathroom ceiling light, and outdoor use
  • SPECIFICATIONS: Dimensions - 1.5" H x 5.3" W; 729 Lumens; Dimmable (Triac dimming) from 100% to 10%; 120V; 90+ CRI; CSA certified to US and Canadian safety standards; IC Rated; Maintains 70% output at 50,000 hours; 3-year limited warranty

Product Description

The Juno 4 inch adjustable downlight with 5CCT switchable white technology provides high-quality light output and efficiency featuring a switch for easy color temperature adjustment to choose between 2700K, 3000K, 3500K, 4000K, or 5000K. The canless design eliminates the need for recessed housings, making it easy to install and requires less labor. The adjustable gimbal allows for up to 20 degrees of rotation, making this version perfect for angled ceilings.
